*******************pin Map****************
ESP32 Pin	Connected To	Function
GPIO 32	    Push Button	    Input (with pull-up)
GPIO 16	    LED	            Output
GPIO 17  	Buzzer	        Output
GPIO 21	    OLED SDA	    I2C Data
GPIO 22	    OLED SCL	     I2C Clock